# 🧱 STEP 6 — ADD TOOLTIP (BUSINESS INFO)

```js
tooltip: {
  formatter: params => {
    const data = params.data;

    return `
      <b>${data.name}</b><br/>
      Role: ${data.role || "N/A"}<br/>
      Department: ${data.department || "N/A"}
    `;
  }
}
```

---

# 🧱 STEP 7 — COLOR BY CATEGORY (DEPARTMENT)

---

## IMPLEMENT

```js
itemStyle: {
  color: params => {
    const dept = params.data.department;

    const map = {
      Engineering: "#3B82F6",
      HR: "#22C55E",
      Operations: "#F59E0B"
    };

    return map[dept] || "#6366F1";
  }
}
```

